description:
Alfons Trekner - The thirteenth collection

This is one of the first "Art Satire" - Projects in the Cryptospace.

This "Alfons Trekner"-Collection again shows the development from the Basic Alfons Trekner without many effects to the final picture of this collection wich has lots of artefacts and effects.

5 Steps - 5 beautiful unique pictures.

This is a rare collection.

And it is cheap. Each Alfons costs 11,11 Mi only.

Please take note that the royalty level is 55%

Check out the details of the final version!

The way of creation is the artists secret.

This is the thirteens collection of our lovely Alfons Trekner. This is the last collection. 

Alfons Trekner will live forever. In the tangle.

Maybe some special Alfons will be made in future. But no more collections.

Hope you enjoyed this project!
1 Alfons per person only!
name: Alfons Trekner - The thirteenth collection - the very last collection
